title: Non-Steam Counter-Strike 1.6 v42 + BOTS Full Install v2
description:
Counter-Strike v42 Build 4554 Changelog : 16 Jul 2009

-------------------------------------
Version 2 Release 14 Jul 2014
-------------------------------------
- Uses REVOLUTiON Emulator 9.85
- Fixed Game crash while user is disconnected
- Fixed BOTS Placements
- Amxmodx v1.80 & v1.81 Compatible

Half-Life Engine
- Added -sys_ticrate command line option to allowed forced override of ticrate
- Prevent more cases of server redirection

Counter-Strike/Condition Zero
- Added -nobots option to allow forced override of bots on servers

Emulator provided by REVOLUTiON
BOTS provided by Wendigo10
Server list provided by Setti.info
Installer created by Zerotech

Visit Website for support http://cs.rin.ru/eng

Remember to seed once you have finished downloading.
